    <span style="font-family: 微软雅黑;color: rgb(96, 98, 102);letter-spacing: 0;font-size: 16px">3.1.2在您进行电子文件签署的同时，</span><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑;color: rgb(96, 98, 102);letter-spacing: 0;font-size: 16px"><span style="font-family:微软雅黑">签必果</span></span><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑;color: rgb(96, 98, 102);letter-spacing: 0;font-size: 16px"><span style="font-family:微软雅黑">平台会为该份电子文件加盖时间戳，确定每次电子签名的签约时间。</span></span>
</p>
<p style=";text-indent: 32px;padding: 0;line-height: 22px;background: rgb(255, 255, 255)">
    <span style="font-family: 微软雅黑;color: rgb(96, 98, 102);letter-spacing: 0;font-size: 16px">&nbsp;</span>
</p>
<p style="margin: 0 0 0 28px;text-indent: 32px;padding: 0;line-height: 22px;background: rgb(255, 255, 255)">
    <span style="font-family: 微软雅黑;color: rgb(96, 98, 102);letter-spacing: 0;font-size: 16px">3.1.3 </span><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑;color: rgb(96, 98, 102);letter-spacing: 0;font-size: 16px"><span style="font-family:微软雅黑">签必果</span></span><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑;color: rgb(96, 98, 102);letter-spacing: 0;font-size: 16px"><span style="font-family:微软雅黑">确保您在平台上制作的电子签名制作数据专属于您所有并由您控制。</span></span>
</p>
<p style=";text-indent: 32px;padding: 0;line-height: 22px;background: rgb(255, 255, 255)">
    <span style="font-family: 微软雅黑;color: rgb(96, 98, 102);letter-spacing: 0;font-size: 16px">&nbsp;</span>
</p>
<p style=";text-indent: 32px;padding: 0;line-height: 22px;background: rgb(255, 255, 255)">
    <span style="font-family: 微软雅黑;color: rgb(96, 98, 102);letter-spacing: 0;font-size: 16px">3.2存证出证服务</span>
</p>
<p style=";text-indent: 32px;padding: 0;line-height: 22px;background: rgb(255, 255, 255)">
    <span style="font-family: 微软雅黑;color: rgb(96, 98, 102);letter-spacing: 0;font-size: 16px">&nbsp;</span>
</p>
<p style="margin: 0 0 0 28px;text-indent: 32px;padding: 0;line-height: 22px;background: rgb(255, 255, 255)">
    <span style="font-family: 微软雅黑;color: rgb(96, 98, 102);letter-spacing: 0;font-size: 16px">3.2.1为了确保后期您的电子合同能更具有证明力，您授权</span><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑;color: rgb(96, 98, 102);letter-spacing: 0;font-size: 16px"><span style="font-family:微软雅黑">签必果</span></span><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑;color: rgb(96, 98, 102);letter-spacing: 0;font-size: 16px"><span style="font-family:微软雅黑">平台收集固定您的签署信息，包括但不限于操作账号的设备信息、网络信息、系统日志、签署人身份信息、签署方式等数据。</span></span>
</p>
<p style=";text-indent: 32px;padding: 0;line-height: 22px;background: rgb(255, 255, 255)">
    <span style="font-family: 微软雅黑;color: rgb(96, 98, 102);letter-spacing: 0;font-size: 16px">&nbsp;</span>
</p>
<p style="margin: 0 0 0 28px;text-indent: 32px;padding: 0;line-height: 22px;background: rgb(255, 255, 255)">
    <span style="font-family: 微软雅黑;color: rgb(96, 98, 102);letter-spacing: 0;font-size: 16px">3.2.2经您签署后的电子文件以及签署信息实时同步传输至</span><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑;color: rgb(96, 98, 102);letter-spacing: 0;font-size: 16px"><span style="font-family:微软雅黑">签必果</span></span><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑;color: rgb(96, 98, 102);letter-spacing: 0;font-size: 16px"><span style="font-family:微软雅黑">的存证系统，并实时采用时间戳技术进行固定；</span></span>
</p>
<p style=";text-indent: 32px;padding: 0;line-height: 22px;background: rgb(255, 255, 255)">
    <span style="font-family: 微软雅黑;color: rgb(96, 98, 102);letter-spacing: 0;font-size: 16px">&nbsp;</span>
</p>
<p style="margin: 0 0 0 28px;text-indent: 32px;padding: 0;line-height: 22px;background: rgb(255, 255, 255)">
    <span style="font-family: 微软雅黑;color: rgb(96, 98, 102);letter-spacing: 0;font-size: 16px">3.2.3经固定后的电子文件或签署信息，您可以通过</span><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑;color: rgb(96, 98, 102);letter-spacing: 0;font-size: 16px"><span style="font-family:微软雅黑">签必果</span></span><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑;color: rgb(96, 98, 102);letter-spacing: 0;font-size: 16px"><span style="font-family:微软雅黑">平台出具电子版或纸质版本的证据报告，证明电子文件以及签署过程的真实性。</span></span>
</p>
<p style=";text-indent: 32px;padding: 0;line-height: 22px;background: rgb(255, 255, 255)">
    <span style="font-family: 微软雅黑;color: rgb(96, 98, 102);letter-spacing: 0;font-size: 16px">&nbsp;</span>
</p>
<p style=";text-indent: 32px;padding: 0;line-height: 22px;background: rgb(255, 255, 255)">
    <span style="font-family: 微软雅黑;color: rgb(96, 98, 102);letter-spacing: 0;font-size: 16px">3.3法律服务</span>
</p>
<p style=";text-indent: 32px;padding: 0;line-height: 22px;background: rgb(255, 255, 255)">
    <span style="font-family: 微软雅黑;color: rgb(96, 98, 102);letter-spacing: 0;font-size: 16px">&nbsp;</span>
</p>
<p style="margin: 0 0 0 28px;text-indent: 32px;padding: 0;line-height: 22px;background: rgb(255, 255, 255)">
    <span style="font-family: 微软雅黑;color: rgb(96, 98, 102);letter-spacing: 0;font-size: 16px">3.3.1您授权</span><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑;color: rgb(96, 98, 102);letter-spacing: 0;font-size: 16px"><span style="font-family:微软雅黑">签必果</span></span><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑;color: rgb(96, 98, 102);letter-spacing: 0;font-size: 16px"><span style="font-family:微软雅黑">将您签署的电子文件同步传输至第三方公证处，您可以通过</span></span><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑;color: rgb(96, 98, 102);letter-spacing: 0;font-size: 16px"><span style="font-family:微软雅黑">签必果</span></span><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑;color: rgb(96, 98, 102);letter-spacing: 0;font-size: 16px"><span style="font-family:微软雅黑">的存证平台申请出具公证书，证明电子文件自存储至公证处之日起未被篡改的证明。</span></span>
</p>
<p style=";text-indent: 32px;padding: 0;line-height: 22px;background: rgb(255, 255, 255)">
    <span style="font-family: 微软雅黑;color: rgb(96, 98, 102);letter-spacing: 0;font-size: 16px">&nbsp;</span>
</p>
<p style="margin: 0 0 0 28px;text-indent: 32px;padding: 0;line-height: 22px;background: rgb(255, 255, 255)">
    <span style="font-family: 微软雅黑;color: rgb(96, 98, 102);letter-spacing: 0;font-size: 16px">3.3.2您授权</span><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑;color: rgb(96, 98, 102);letter-spacing: 0;font-size: 16px"><span style="font-family:微软雅黑">签必果</span></span><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑;color: rgb(96, 98, 102);letter-spacing: 0;font-size: 16px"><span style="font-family:微软雅黑">将您签署的电子文件哈希值同步传输至第三方司法鉴定中心，您可以通过</span></span><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑;color: rgb(96, 98, 102);letter-spacing: 0;font-size: 16px"><span style="font-family:微软雅黑">签必果</span></span><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑;color: rgb(96, 98, 102);letter-spacing: 0;font-size: 16px"><span style="font-family:微软雅黑">的存证平台申请出具司法鉴定意见书，证明电子文件与电子文件哈希值比对一致性的证明。</span></span>
</p>
<p style=";text-indent: 32px;padding: 0;line-height: 22px;background: rgb(255, 255, 255)">
    <span style="font-family: 微软雅黑;color: rgb(96, 98, 102);letter-spacing: 0;font-size: 16px">&nbsp;</span>
</p>
<p style=";text-indent: 0;padding: 0;line-height: 22px;background: rgb(255, 255, 255)">
    <span style="font-family: 微软雅黑;color: rgb(194, 79, 74);letter-spacing: 0;font-size: 16px"><span style="font-family:微软雅黑">四、服务费用</span></span>
